data.description: Welcome to 220 Roosevelt Ave., Elyria, OH! This charming three-level Colonial home features four bedrooms, one full bathroom, and boasts original and modern charm. With a two-car detached garage, newer carpet, flooring, and fresh paint, it’s an ideal space for a great family home. The main level you will find the living room, dining room and kitchen. Moving to the second level, you will find the homes, one full bathroom and three bedrooms. Moving to the third level you will find a larger space to make your own. Maybe a fourth bedroom, mancave or playroom the options are endless!  Don’t miss out on this inviting property!
